Right now, we do have already some really awesome features that other servers not have.[/i] They will be listed below; [i] - Custom Home - Vote Rewards - Donator Zone - Basic Hunter - 100% Duel Arena - 100% Pest Control - 100% Warrior Guild - 100% Party Room - Perfect Summoning - Perfect Player & NPC Clipping - Perfect Combat System - Autocast in Mage Book - Normal XP Rate - DDoS Server Protection - Encrypted Character Files(Protection) - Great Community Forum - No Lag At All - Playershare - Perfect Item Switching - Ofcourse 24/7 online ~ VPS[/i]
We have much and much more features, just to much to list them up here. We can suggest just to take a look at our server and you will not regret it.
[b]Media[/b]
